"title": "5705: inheritance, spiritual",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5705",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Believers are privileged to receive a spiritual inheritance from their heavenly Father as a result of their adoption into the family of God through faith.</p>\n<h2>Believers have an inheritance in Christ</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ as God's heir</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:2\">HEB 1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:37-Matt21:39\">MAT 21:37–21:39</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:6-Mark12:8\">MRK 12:6–12:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:13-Luke20:15\">LUK 20:13–20:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:18\">MAT 28:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:12\">LUK 19:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:35\">JHN 3:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:4-Heb1:6\">HEB 1:4–1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:7-Ps2:8\">PSA 2:7–2:8</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are co-heirs with Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17\">ROM 8:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:6\">EPH 3:6</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are heirs under the covenant</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:17\">HEB 6:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:15\">HEB 9:15</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are heirs by grace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:18\">GAL 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:32\">ACT 20:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:12\">COL 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are heirs through faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:29\">GAL 3:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:13-Rom4:17\">ROM 4:13–4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:7-Heb11:10\">HEB 11:7–11:10</a></p>\n<h2>The nature of the spiritual inheritance of believers</h2>\n<h3>They inherit salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:14\">HEB 1:14</a></strong></p>\n<h3>They inherit eternal life</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:25\">LUK 10:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:7\">TIT 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:7\">1PE 3:7</a></p>\n<h3>They have the full rights of sons</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:4-Gal4:7\">GAL 4:4–4:7</a></p>\n<h3>They have the rights of the firstborn</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:22-Heb12:23\">HEB 12:22–12:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:22\">EXO 4:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:9\">2KI 2:9</a></p>\n<h3>They inherit the earth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:5\">MAT 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:11\">PSA 37:11</a></p>\n<h3>They inherit the kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34\">MAT 25:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:28-Luke22:30\">LUK 22:28–22:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:21\">REV 3:21</a></p>\n<h3>They inherit all things</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:31\">LUK 15:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:21-1Cor3:22\">1CO 3:21–3:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:7\">REV 21:7</a></p>\n<h3>Their inheritance is the word of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:111\">PSA 119:111</a></p>\n<h3>They inherit the Lord himself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:26\">PSA 73:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:20\">NUM 18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:9\">DEU 10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps142:5\">PSA 142:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:16\">JER 10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:19\">JER 51:19</a></p>\n<h3>It is a good inheritance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:6\">PSA 16:6</a></p>\n<h2>The permanence of believers' spiritual inheritance</h2>\n<h3>It has been prepared from the creation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34\">MAT 25:34</a></p>\n<h3>It is guaranteed for eternity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:3–1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:18\">PSA 37:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:13\">DAN 12:13</a></p>\n<h3>It is sealed with God's promise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13-Eph1:14\">EPH 1:13–1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:3\">REV 7:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:4\">REV 9:4</a></p>\n<h2>The conditions of spiritual inheritance</h2>\n<h3>It is conditional upon continuing obedience and faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:9-1Pet3:12\">1PE 3:9–3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:12-Ps34:16\">PSA 34:12–34:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:12-Ps25:13\">PSA 25:12–25:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:11\">PSA 37:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:29\">PSA 37:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:34\">PSA 37:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps61:5\">PSA 61:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:10\">PRO 28:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:5\">MAT 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:24\">COL 3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:12\">HEB 6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:5\">JAS 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>It is denied to the ungodly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:5\">EPH 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:9\">PSA 37:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:22\">PSA 37:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9-1Cor6:10\">1CO 6:9–6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:1-1Cor10:5\">1CO 10:1–10:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:19-Gal5:21\">GAL 5:19–5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:12-Heb3:19\">HEB 3:12–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:27\">REV 21:27</a></p>",
